Description.SourceString: A standard Assembly Station for production of essential vehicles and equipment. Construction will take time and may be halted if resources are depleted. Some projects require a base vehicle to be present on the Assembly Station before production can begin.
Description.LocalizedString: A standard Assembly Station for production of essential vehicles and equipment. Construction will take time and may be halted if resources are depleted. Some projects require a base vehicle to be present on the Assembly Station before production can begin.

Description.SourceString: An assembly rigged to manufacture parts used in the construction of naval vessels at a Dry Dock.
Description.LocalizedString: An assembly rigged to manufacture parts used in the construction of naval vessels at a Dry Dock.

Description.SourceString: An assembly station for producing light-duty logistics vehicles like trucks.
Description.LocalizedString: An assembly station for producing light-duty logistics vehicles like trucks.

Description.SourceString: An assembly station for producing half-tracks and rocket vehicles.
Description.LocalizedString: An assembly station for producing half-tracks and rocket vehicles.

Description.SourceString: An assembly station for producing field weapons and utility vehicles such as Harvesters.

Description.SourceString: An assembly station for producing tank class vehicles.
Description.LocalizedString: An assembly station for producing tank class vehicles.

Description.SourceString: An assembly station for producing emplaced weapon platforms and specialized tanks.
Description.LocalizedString: An assembly station for producing emplaced weapon platforms and specialized tanks.

Description.SourceString: A workshop platform for the assembly of multi-part long-range ballistic missiles such as the A0E-9, or AEON Rocket.
